---
<!-- Azura Careers CTA: dark green band, full width -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: var(--green-dark);">
  <div class="absolute inset-0">
    <img src="/images/careers-bg.jpg" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-15" loading="lazy"/>
    <div class="absolute inset-0" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(26,61,37,.97) 0%, rgba(45,106,63,.85) 100%);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-8xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-24 lg:py-32">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="reveal">
        <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[.2em] uppercase mb-4 block" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,.55);">Carrières</span>
        <h2 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-semibold text-white leading-tight mb-6 text-balance">
          Nous rejoindre
        </h2>
        <div class="w-12 h-px bg-white/30 mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-white/65 text-base leading-relaxed max-w-md mb-8">
          Rejoignez une équipe de 3 500 passionnés qui façonnent l'agriculture de demain. Nous recrutons des talents dans tous nos métiers, avec une priorité donnée au recrutement local.
        </p>
        <a href="/careers" class="btn-primary" style="background: white; color: var(--green-dark);">
          Voir toutes les offres
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/>
          </svg>
        </a>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal-right grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        {[
          { v: '3 500+', l: 'Collaborateurs' },
          { v: '95%',    l: 'Emplois locaux' },
          { v: '250k h', l: 'Formation / an' },
          { v: '5',      l: 'Pôles de métiers' },
        ].map((s) => (
          <div class="p-6 border border-white/10 hover:border-white/25 transition-colors">
            <p class="font-display text-3xl font-semibold text-white mb-1">{s.v}</p>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">{s.l}</p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
